# Architecture & Code Organization

## Core Principles

### 1. Single Responsibility
Each class/module has ONE clear purpose.

### 2. Loose Coupling
Systems communicate via events, not direct calls.

### 3. Data-Driven Design
Configuration over hardcoding.

