## File Organization

### Keep Files Focused

**Target**: < 200 lines per file
**Refactor at**: 300 lines
**Hard limit**: 400 lines

**When file grows**:
1. Identify distinct responsibilities
2. Extract into separate files
3. Update `docs/architecture/08-directory-structure.md`
4. Update imports

### Example Splits

**Before**: `Renderer.js` (1000 lines)
```javascript
// Everything in one file
class Renderer {
  renderText() { /* 100 lines */ }
  renderShapes() { /* 200 lines */ }
  renderSprites() { /* 300 lines */ }
  renderEffects() { /* 400 lines */ }
}
```

**After**: Split by responsibility
```
/rendering
├── Renderer.js          # Orchestrates rendering (~100 lines)
├── TextRenderer.js      # Text rendering only (~100 lines)
├── ShapeRenderer.js     # Shapes only (~150 lines)
├── SpriteRenderer.js    # Sprites only (~200 lines)
└── EffectRenderer.js    # Effects only (~250 lines)
```

